description:
Newly Renovated Modern Brooklyn Loft, in a factory building with the greatest rooftop to relax, next to the renowned Brooklyn Bridge to take a stroll over in a nice day.
What else can one ask for... 
Great for a couples vacation, or with your family, or just a business trip.
24 Hours coffee and tea.
Full kitchen with utensils.

I'm always a phone call away if you need me, you can reach me on my personal cell that will be provided to you upon arrival.

Downtown Brooklyn, next to the Brooklyn, and Manhattan Bridges.

5 Minutes walk to all the subway lines to get around Manhattan, or Brooklyn.

This apartment is on the 3rd floor.
The hip commercial elevator hours are Monday - Saturday 11am to 11pm
Sundays 12 noon to 10pm
All other hours please note that you will need to use the stairs.
The Laundry Room is in the basement.

hosts.about:
Hola! We are Lizbeth & Gabby, two bestfriends who are open to share our beautiful apartment/ studio all for yourself ! 
When you come to NY the first thing you need is a comfy bed and we promise to give you that and more. 
We are 3 minutes away from the Manhattan and Brooklyn bridge, dumbo is also near where you can enjoy the view of the beautiful sunset and city, you will love it ! 
We offer many amenities and we will love to suggest many more places for you to visit here in NY.
Don't think twice about it ! We will be waiting for you!
